import React from 'react'
import { Container, Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap'

function Footer() {
  return (

      <footer className='c-black'>
        <Container>
          <Row>
            <Col className='text-center py-3'>Copyright © ErnestoGarozzo</Col>
            </Row>
        </Container>
      </footer>
    
  )
}

export default Footer
